io.purush.java.immutable.collections

Interface List<E>


  • public interface List<E>
    A simplistic abstraction of immutable Lists.
    Ability to add, remove, update elements to/from the List.
    Additional ability to merge, split, piece-out lists from a List.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Purush Swaminathan
